{"tid":820765,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日8號風球，港股停市一天","createTime":"2018-09-15T15:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T15:33:24.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f98423ad0ea8fabe60c29c5b14fe0bb73d03142c","tid":820765,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"對於股民來說，聽日股市安排同樣重要，根據港交所（388）證券及衍生產品市場的交易安排，若八號風球在上午7時或之前解除，將如常進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n若上午7時至9時八號風球除下，開市前時段將被取消，早上交易時段則在風球解除後兩小時恢復交易，開始時間須為整點或30分，例如若風球在上午7:15解除，早上交易時段將於上午9:30開始。<br />\n<br />\n若上午9時後至11時期間風球解除，上午整段交易時段將被取消，下午交易時段將如常於下午1:00開始。<br />\n<br />\n上午11時至11時半解除風球，交易時段將於下午1:30開始。上午11:30後至中午12:00期間解除風球，交易時段將於下午2:00開始。<br />\n<br />\n至於中午12時後始解除風球全日停止交易。<br />\n<br />\n聽日個山竹好大機會打足全日，港股極有可能停市一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760fd3cd51bb832268480cb5fbf73bf32c39c332","tid":820765,"uid":205396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"0/100"},{"pid":"61561936f9e5ead4df667f004b427a1ddd7604a8","tid":820765,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8055a703c7e92bee08f06d83227e0d6fb477a9bc","tid":820765,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07468780881a18f41e35ce99577a60f226e8dc3c","tid":820765,"uid":188542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"星期日有股票?<br />\n<br />\nYou are gonna be joking."},{"pid":"843dedf2eef23c562fbad6104e156f9e270d2e3d","tid":820765,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64273d4d7c945450d042b74ed820643bbb90e78","tid":820765,"uid":123613,"like":0